  &lt;p id="9lHQk4"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket&lt;/em&gt; has been a big hit since its &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/30/24283488/pokemon-tcg-pocket-is-finally-here"&gt;worldwide launch last month&lt;/a&gt;, and the team behind it has shared a brief roadmap of a couple updates to come — including the ability to trade cards with other people.&lt;/p&gt;
