    <title>Twinkly’s smart holiday string lights have dropped to a new low price </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="A lit up Christmas tree in a living room." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ETbIErwciFXZsKapZgvMAAxpfWw=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723747/twinklylifestylepic.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;Twinkly’s colorful string lights are more than half off at Amazon.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;
