    <title>CFPB is reportedly trying to put Google under bank-like supervision </title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="Dollars float through pillars, as if to exit a bank" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/H_nJDcm2ohGdzVhiL2X6y99KQF4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723474/STK417_H_Herrera_Money_03.0.jpg" /&gt;
